Privacy Policy for DenTool: 
DenTool operates the DenTool mobile application, a platform designed to help dentists and dental clinics browse and request dental supplies. 
This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our application. 
By using the DenTool app, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy 
• Information We Collect 
We may collect the following types of information: 
Personal Information 
When you create an account or use the application, we may collect: 
• Full name  
• Phone number  
• Email address (if provided)  
• Clinic name  
• Professional information related to dentistry  
Usage Information 
We may automatically collect information such as: 
• device type  
• operating system  
• app usage data  
• interaction within the application  
This information helps us improve the functionality and performance of DenTool 
• How We Use Your Information 
We use the collected information to: 
• create and manage user accounts  
• process product requests and orders  
• communicate with users regarding orders or services  
• improve application performance and user experience  
• provide technical support  
• prevent misuse or fraudulent activity 
 
 
• Sharing of Information 
DenTool does not sell or rent your personal information. 
We may share limited information with: 
• suppliers or partners in order to fulfill product requests  
• service providers who help operate the application  
• authorities if required by law  
Any shared information will only be used for service-related purposes 
• Data Security 
We take reasonable steps to protect your information from: 
• unauthorized access  
• misuse  
• disclosure  
However, no digital platform can guarantee complete security 
• Data Retention 
We retain your information only as long as necessary to: 
• maintain your account  
• provide services through the application  
• comply with legal obligations  
Users may request account deletion at any time. 
• User Rights 
Users may request to: 
